you feel reassured

262
00:24:34,990 --> 00:24:36,950
因为你知道你刚才看到的不会发生在你身上。
because you know what you just saw can't happen to you.

263
00:24:37,090 --> 00:24:39,020
不是用哭泣和低语。
Not with Cries and Whispers.

264
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:42,130
孤独，痛苦，死亡的恐惧。
The solitude, the agony, the horror of dying.

265
00:24:42,270 --> 00:24:43,510
事情就是这样。
It's the way things are.

266
00:24:43,650 --> 00:24:45,720
不,它不是。这是一个梦。
No, it's not. It's a dream.

267
00:24:45,860 --> 00:24:48,070
或者更像是一场噩梦。
Or more like a fucking nightmare.

268
00:24:48,210 --> 00:24:50,970
我只希望他的生活比他的电影更有趣。
I just hope he had more fun in his life than in his movies.

269
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:52,870
我也是。
Me too.

270
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:58,110
为什么他的角色总是那么糟糕?
Why are his characters always so awful?

271
00:24:58,250 --> 00:25:01,080
为什么他从来没有表现出任何温柔或轻松?
Why doesn't he ever show any tenderness or lightness?

272
00:25:01,220 --> 00:25:03,600
范妮和亚历山大有很多。
There's loads in Fanny and Alexander.

273
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:05,260
没错，但为时已晚。
True, but that came late.

274
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,910
是啊，不过晚了也挺好的，对吧?
Yeah, but it's good that it came late, right?

275
00:25:07,050 --> 00:25:08,740
他对变轻不感兴趣。
He wasn't interested in being light.

276
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:11,540
他很黑暗，他想探索这一点。
He--he was dark, and he wanted to explore that.

277
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:12,820
这对他来说很有趣。
It was fun for him.

278
00:25:14,020 --> 00:25:15,580
为什么他一次也没有
Why didn't he ever once

279
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:17,030
想探索——
want to explore--

280
00:25:17,170 --> 00:25:19,200
幸福吗?-是的,幸福!
