His houses, the island, beautiful landscapes.

283
00:25:25,210 --> 00:25:28,420
一切都没有他电影里那么残酷。
Everything is less harsh than in his movies.

284
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:30,590
那就他妈一月再来这里试试。
Then try this place in fucking January.

285
