but in the end, they do you good.

290
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:49,750
他不?-不。
-His don't? -No.

291
00:25:49,890 --> 00:25:51,100
只是伤害我。
Just hurt me.

292
00:25:51,230 --> 00:25:52,820
那你为什么还要看?
Then why do you watch them then?

293
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,930
因为我爱他们。
Because I love them.

294
00:25:55,070 --> 00:25:58,140
我只是不知道为什么，就这样。
I just don't know why, that's all.

