[cheers and whistles]

315
00:27:44,660 --> 00:27:47,900
让我们再次欢迎安东尼·桑德斯。
[Berit] And please welcome again Anthony Sanders.

316
00:27:51,870 --> 00:27:53,360
[托尼]在我的一生中，
[Tony] All of my life,

317
00:27:53,490 --> 00:27:55,910
我觉得我就像在走钢丝，
I felt like I was, um, on a tightrope,

318
00:27:56,050 --> 00:27:59,400
你知道，我一直在平衡，
you know, I was kind of balancing,

319
00:27:59,530 --> 00:28:01,610
如果我掉下来，如果我掉下来，我就
and, uh, if I fell-- if I fell off, I just--

